\&\fB\*(rqX\-Face:\*(rqs mit slrnface Anzeigen (use_slrnface)\fP
If enabled \fBtin\fP uses \fB\%slrnface\fP(1)  to interpret the \*(rqX\-Face:\*(rq
header. For this option to have any effect, \fBtin\fP must be running in an
